.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "21 avril 2025" "1.0" "Holberton Simple Shell"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- simple UNIX command interpreter

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh

.SH DESCRIPTION
A minimal shell written in C. It reads user input, parses it, and executes commands using the PATH. Works in interactive and non-interactive mode.

.SH BUILTINS
.TP
.B exit
Exit the shell.
.TP
.B env
Print the current environment.

.SH EXAMPLES
Start shell:
.EX
$ ./hsh
.EX

Run a command:
.EX
$ ls -la
.EX

Exit:
.EX
$ exit
.EX

.SH AUTHOR
Nina Galasso and Myriam Mezhoud
